"The user starts with the parallel coordinates overview (View 1) to identify high-impact players through performance score ranges. Brushing interactions filter these players into the scatter plot matrix (View 2) revealing direct metric-outcome relationships, and the faceted bars (View 3) showing fantasy point consistency. Selections in View 2 propagate to the geospatial heatmap (View 4) exposing venue-specific success patterns, while View 3's insights feed into density plots (View 5) analyzing career consistency correlations."